-- GM ready to cut N. American production if needed
-- 
-- Tue Feb 12, 2008 11:46am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/02/12/us-gm-cfo-capacity-idUSN1223273220080212

 

 DETROIT  (Reuters) - General Motors Corp is ready to cut North American production if economic conditions warrant, but has not changed its overall forecast for the year, Chief Financial Officer Fritz Henderson said on Tuesday. 

 (Reporting by  David Bailey ; Editing by  Derek Caney )